scenarioInformation.title: Consistency and Standards
scenarioInformation.description:
While it is important to maintain standards across different UIs internally, it is also important to maintain external consistency with user interfaces the user is already familiar with.

Atomic Clothing is looking to design a new e-commerce website as they have received complaints that their previous one is not easy to understand. They want a website similar to Amazon.com, Walmart.com, and Nike.com. 

Create a website that maintains external consistency with other e-commerce websites that users will be able to intuitively understand.
